byline.contributor: Lori Rotenberk and Dirk Johnson contributed reporting from Moline, Ill.; Christina Capecchi and Sheila Eldred from Minnesota and Susanne Craig and Jeremy B. Merrill from New York.
byline.original: By JOHN ELIGON and SERGE F. KOVALESKI

abstract: Investigators are looking into why Prince’s private plane made unscheduled landing for medical emergency in Moline, Ill, just few days before his death.

headline.print_headline: Piecing Together the Clues to Prince’s Final Days
headline.main: Clues to the Mystery of Prince’s Final Days

snippet: Prince’s private plane made an emergency landing a few days before his death. Investigators are looking into the distress call that led to the stop.
lead_paragraph: Prince’s private plane made an emergency landing a few days before his death. Investigators are looking into the distress call that led to the stop.
